Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.65,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você pulsam intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.28,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.49,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.86,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos vínculos inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.07,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.80,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.76,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:43.35,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e ondule-as...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:50.23,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.19,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.57,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.87,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para qual futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.37,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.38,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você pulsam intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.22,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.55,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos vínculos inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.80,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.85,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.64,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:33.28,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}já decidimos isso há muito tempo.
