Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:38.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama, chegou \NSmoothie-sama, a general doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.84,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1136,430.429)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(300,0)}WHOLE CAKE\N CHÂTEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:49.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Logo chegará Katakuri-sama, o general doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, faz muito tempo que os três não se reúnem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E Cracker?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ainda não voltou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:01.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com certeza chegará logo com\N a cabeça de Chapéu de Palha como presente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:04.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou morrendo de ansiedade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:19.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:20.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão Cracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele é um general doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem fez isso?!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou matá-lo!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:02.20,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(410,0)}MINISTRO DO QUEIJO (19° FILHO DA FAMÍLIA CHARLOTTE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:02.20,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(410,0)}CHARLOTTE MONT D'OR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:06.60,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(410,362)}MINISTRO DA CREME (QUINTO FILHO DA FAMÍLIA CHARLOTTE)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:06.60,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(410,362)}CHARLOTTE OPERA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De onde ele veio voando-fa?!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:07.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não me engano, nosso irmão...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:11.16,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(410,0)}MINISTRA DA MANTEIGA - 18ª FILHA DA FAMÍLIA CHARLOTTE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:11.16,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(410,0)}CHARLOTTE GALETTE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:11.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...foi para a floresta ontem à noite \Npara aniquilar o Chapéu de Palha Luffy.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:19.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...que o Chapéu de Palha Luffy está perto-fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Alerta de emergência!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Evacuem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:34.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Derrotaram o Cracker, o general doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:46.51,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(142.857,430.143)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(400,400)}FLORESTA\N SEDUTORA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Comi uma porção vitalícia de biscoitos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas você encolheu muito, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:05.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gear Fourth consome energia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pound!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde você estava?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:15.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, desculpe por fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pensei que vocês perderiam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que sincero você é!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:23.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É que o oponente era um \Ndos três generais doces...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, vencemos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Animem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:45.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Derrotamos um oficial de uma Yonkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,N-Não consigo me mover...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:50.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que fizemos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:55.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ajudamos na derrota\N de Cracker-sama-ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:02.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todos sabem que a Vivre Card de mama é muito poderosa contra nós, os homies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:10.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso os filhos de mama \Nsão proibidos de possuir uma!{\fad(0,679)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você tem uma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora entendo o valor dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas isso é grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:29.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando derrotaram Snack, o general doce,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:35.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,o exército vingativo de Cracker \Nfez o mar ficar negro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e Linlin, furiosa, criou uma tempestade...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:46.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ouvi dizer que afundaram o navio\Ninimigo em um piscar de olhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma tempestade?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:51.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin está acompanhada pelo clima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pelo clima?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Na mão esquerda dela está \NZeus, a nuvem de tempestade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:00.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Na mão direita dela, \NPrometheus, o sol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:06.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ninguém pode deter \Nmama quando ela fica brava.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:12.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fujam antes que ela descubra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então que ela fique brava!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu é que deveria estar bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Primeiro, aquele maldito Sanji...!
Comment: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.38,Captions,,0,0,0,,Para os companheiros, preciso\Nver uma mulher. Voltarei.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.38,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2980,3480)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.38,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2980,3480)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.38,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2980,3480)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.38,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2980,3480)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.38,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2980,3480)}Para os companheiros. Vou ver uma mulher, voltarei aconteça o que acontecer. Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De repente desaparece\N deixando uma nota!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sem nos dizer o porquê!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.97,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É meu problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.23,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Aconteça o que acontecer, voltarei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:44.06,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Saúdem eles por mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Graças ao mapa de Pudding\N conseguimos chegar até aqui,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:49.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,mas Pekoms desapareceu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:53.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e, embora Pudding \Ndissesse que traria Sanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:57.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,não havia ninguém na costa\N onde combinamos de nos encontrar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:00.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Perdemos muito tempo\N nos perdendo nesta floresta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:06.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se eles se casarem, Sanji será\N subordinado de Big Mom, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há tempo a perder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando será o casamento?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele disse que os Vinsmoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...iriam hoje ao castelo\N onde será o casamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que horas são?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Temos que evitar \Nque entrem no castelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,V-Você está falando sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não fugirem, de verdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, árvore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você sabe onde fica o castelo, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:45.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:48.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me leve até o castelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:57.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos recuperar Sanji \Ncuste o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami, você me escuta? {SC807-808 4:22:46}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:29.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se tudo der certo, vamos \Nnos encontrar com vocês, Brook e...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não parece que estão bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:33.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:37.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, não podem \Nnos salvar de fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Continuem avançan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami, não se preocupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como não vou me preocupar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, vamos ao \Ncastelo buscar Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:50.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De acordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando o recuperarem, \Nnos avisem por este espelho...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele quebrou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Alô?! Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Carrot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Virou um espelho normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles estarão bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele perdeu peso?! {SC807-808 8:29:94}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:18.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:25.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já está quase voltando ao normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O corpo humano funciona assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Carne...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Carne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, garota.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você tem sorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles estão lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o Germa 66.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você vê o Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:55.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sua Majestade, alguém está vindo aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse cara atravessou todo \No território e chegou até aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E aquela árvore enorme atrás dele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele está correndo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que bom que chegamos a tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:21.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pensei que não te veria de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:25.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que vocês estão aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:29.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse é o Chapéu de Palha Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viemos te buscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:33.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare, maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O gato vai virar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Na carta você disse que \Nvoltaria, mas não quis esperar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:47.47,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,387)}É uma festa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:52.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pensava em vir sozinho, mas assim não...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:55.11,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você disse que suas mãos eram importantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:12:00.00,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Se tentar sair desta ilha, \Nsuas mãos explodirão!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:07.17,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,435)}Se alguém recusar um convite de mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então Zoro e os outros já\N devem estar no País de Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.83,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(232,480)}"Você se importa se o matarmos?".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso vim com Nami, Chopper e Brook te buscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:22.30,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você é um sacrifício, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.06,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu não mudei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.94,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Mas se você se desviar do \Ncaminho da masculinidade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.57,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,eu me matarei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.97,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sanji, comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:34.92,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não te considero meu filho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.51,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É o que os pais devem pagar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:39.94,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É uma desgraça que \Nnão quero que ninguém saiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.92,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.97,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ei, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.69,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}Cuide-se dos resfriados.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, de qualquer forma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Sanji-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sumam daqui, piratas de segunda categoria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:16.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Vinsmoke Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um príncipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...do Reino Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe por ter escondido isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:28.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês pareceriam patéticos se eu tivesse contado.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:33.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossas posições são \Ncompletamente opostas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:38.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aqui posso gastar dinheiro e\N usar soldados e criados à vontade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:43.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Voltar para aquele barco estúpido com seus companheiros...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:49.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...ou viver casado com a \Nbela filha de Big Mom, a Yonkou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:54.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É óbvio onde serei mais feliz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não leve aquela carta a sério.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:00.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou voltar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que vocês conseguiram chegar até aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:05.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sumam daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como é mesmo seu nome?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não enche!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não concordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, vou te ajudar afugentando eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se meta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...vou afugentá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como assim afugentar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sumam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não significa outra coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:47.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não sei por que você veio,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:50.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,mas obrigado pelo esforço.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:56.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas se realmente se importassem comigo, teriam feito o oposto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Em vez de ficar com vocês, \Nque são pobres e insignificantes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:04.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,prefiro pertencer aos Piratas de Big Mom, que são mais ricos e poderosos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Serei feliz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:13.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Até duvido que você será o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É natural apostar no cavalo vencedor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:20.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare de brincar, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:27.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, durante todo esse tempo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,você esteve me enganando.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, é isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, eu te desprezava.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E esse brilho?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:43.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chamas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:47.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece que veremos algo interessante.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:53.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sei que será difícil aceitar \Na verdade tão repentinamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou te mostrar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:56.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Prepare-se.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun, espe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Joue Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.76,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2980,3480)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.76,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2980,3480)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.76,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2980,3480)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.76,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2980,3480)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.76,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2980,3480)}Tiro na bochecha {translated it myself}
Comment: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.76,Note,,0,0,0,,Cheek Shot{\fad(250,250)}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está sangrando!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun, sério...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Prepare-se.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:56.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Use Haki ou morrerá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero falar com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que precisaria de Haki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...lutar contra você!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...desapareça!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Também me recuso a isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você sempre foi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:36.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...egoísta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.01,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ei, cozinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:59.57,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1224)}Você gostaria de ser meu companheiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:02.36,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)}Você será o cozinheiro do \Nnosso navio pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só viemos te buscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:17.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...lutou contra um oficial \Ninimigo a noite toda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O corpo dele já...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já chega, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não diga nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...é um duelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como assim duelo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:40.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:13.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desapareça da minha vista de uma vez por todas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desapareça!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desapareça!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desapareça de uma vez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...da minha vista!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu me recuso!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá vou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:16.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já chega...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:32.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vamos embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:51.35,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,766)}Você é um bom cozinheiro, \Nvem comigo e sejamos piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:59.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Concassé!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:59.07,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2980,3480)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.67,0:21:59.07,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2980,3480)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:21:55.67,0:21:59.07,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2980,3480)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.67,0:21:59.07,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2980,3480)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:55.67,0:21:59.07,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2980,3480)}Esmagar {translated it myself}
Comment: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:59.07,Note,,0,0,0,,Crush{\fad(250,250)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:20.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que poder de combate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:28.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como era de se esperar de um Vinsmoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.63,0:22:38.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:39.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:40.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Resista!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:42.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:54.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:02.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Adeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:03.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:05.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,nunca deveríamos ter vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:06.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:07.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que mulher intensa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:08.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu adoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:22.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Finalmente se livrou \Ndesses laços inúteis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:24.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe a espera.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:26.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:27.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:37.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:44.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:46.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:55.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como assim pirata de segunda categoria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:58.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não diga palavras que você não quer dizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:24:00.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não minta!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:05.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você achou que poderia \Nme afugentar com isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:07.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não encha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:11.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por mais que você me chute,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:13.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,quem está sofrendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:18.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}...é você!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.94,0:24:29.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.08,0:24:30.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.03,0:24:32.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não importa a razão, \Nele não deveria fazer isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:33.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.22,0:24:36.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Paramos aqui, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:39.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Continuem avançando.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:48.71,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.38,0:24:52.00,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você já ouviu falar do All Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.00,0:24:54.20,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,518)}É um oceano milagroso.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.99,0:24:56.68,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Naquele oceano...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.25,0:25:01.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossa jornada...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.06,0:25:04.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...ainda continua!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.21,0:25:09.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou te esperar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.65,0:25:14.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você não voltar, eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.67,0:25:16.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}...vou morrer de fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.72,0:25:22.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Porque você é o cozinheiro do meu navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.12,0:25:26.40,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(402,431)}Ele estava fazendo comida para ratos de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.88,0:25:32.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só vou comer sua comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.59,0:25:38.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que eu passe fome ou seja atingido por lanças,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.87,0:25:43.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,vou te esperar sem me mover daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.10,0:26:02.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Volte aconteça o que acontecer, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.12,0:26:07.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sem você...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.94,0:26:12.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}...não poderei ser o Rei dos Piratas!
